This property has been on "hold" since first week it was on the market.
Welcomed to this cute three bedroom brick ranch in Forest Hills. Move in ready. New roof 2018. New heat/air complete unit 2022. Refrigerator remains and is only one year old. Fenced back yard with covered patio. Well maintained. Conveniently located...Priced to sell. Call for appointment to see.
